snippet: Complexions Contemporary Ballet started off its two-week stint at the Joyce with a packed, two-and-a-half hour bill.
abstract: Claudia La Rocco reviews performance by Complexions Contemporary Ballet, including a premiere by choreographer Camille A Brown, at the Joyce Theater.
